  <steps>
    <step order="1">Author `ComposerActionBar.tsx`:
      - Props per prompt
      - Early return `null` if `mount === 'inline'`
      - Switch on `mode` to render the correct button set
      - Send is `appearance='primary'`, others `appearance='subtle'` or default
      - Send shows `&lt;Spinner /&gt;` when `isSending`
      - Save Draft disabled when `!isDirty`
      - Bottom-right layout for `page`; dialog footer layout for `dialog`</step>
    <step order="2">Wire into engine's `ActionsRegion` slot in `EmailComposer.tsx` — engine passes mode, mount, isSending, isDirty, and callbacks that dispatch reducer actions or invoke imperative handle stubs.</step>
    <step order="3">Update `EmailComposer/index.ts` — export `ComposerActionBar`.</step>
    <step order="4">Smoke test all 5 modes in dev: verify correct button set; verify inline mount → no bar rendered.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `npm run build` + `npm run lint` clean.</step>
    <step order="6">Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 019 ✅.</step>
    <step order="7">Update `current-task.md` per task-execute protocol.</step>
  </steps>

